dct_description_sm: A georeferenced map showing a portion of the the area in Humboldt County, California downstream of the Trinity Dam that would be flooded in the event of a failure (breach) or uncontrolled release of water. This map is one of five showing the complete inundation area. It was downloaded from http://www.humboldtgov.org/276/GIS-Data-Download on October 3, 2014.
